---
title: Maple-Orange Glazed Double Duck Breasts with Herby Potatoes and Arugula Side Salad
description: This plate is a taste of Canadian bounty! Maple syrup, grainy mustard and rich duck make for a luxurious trio, while thyme-roasted potatoes meet their perfect match with rendered duck drippings.
